After attending Gravesend Grammar School for Girls on Pelham Road in Gravesend attending a performance arts course, she trained at the Royal Academy of Dramatic Art on a full grant.
Arterton appears in a number of forthcoming film and television productions, including the next James Bond film, Quantum of Solace.
When it launches in October 2008 she will be the face of Avon's Bond Girl 007 fragrance.
